  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversea the budget sheet of project(s) under your care and make timely reports to the Managing Director periodically on the profit and attendance.</li><li>Ensure monthly/weekly progress and safety reports are submitted on time.</li><li> Liaises closely with the different stakeholders, namely clients, architects, consultants, main contractor, sub contractors, specialists and relevant authorities to ensure the smooth and timely execution of project deliverables.</li></ul><ul><li>Work out any costs saving in term of value of engineering and presenting it to the Managing Director before making submission to the client.</li></ul><ul><li>Provide necessary comparisons and recommendations on short listed vendors, Subcons and Specialists before final confirmation by the Managing Director.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure all works are carried out in accordance and compliance with the project specifications, codes, standard and regulations.</li></ul><ul><li>Manage all team members and ensure the deliver daily works to meet project requirements.</li></ul><ul><li>Manage and submit all variation costs and monitor project closely to ensure variation cost confirmation before awarding of work of claims made by Sub-Contractors and Vendor.</li></ul><ul><li>Report Project Progress to the Management Director and Work at any project assigned to you by the Company.</li></ul><ul><li>Manage and ensure all progress claims are submitted in timely manner.</li></ul><ul><li>Report any major concerns and /or impacts of projects matters to the Managing Director.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
